longBusinessSummary: Tian Shan Development (Holding) Limited, an investment holding company, engages in the development and sale of real estate properties in the People's Republic of China. Its principal property projects include medium- to high-end villas, condominiums, duplexes, and residential units in multi-story buildings, as well as integrated projects for developing private industries by small and medium enterprises in the Bohai Economic Rim. The company offers its projects under the Tian Shan brand. The company was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Shijiazhuang, the People's Republic of China. Tian Shan Development (Holding) Limited is a subsidiary of Neway Enterprises Limited.
